<h5>Panel Figure <code>.sage-panel__figure</code></h5>
<p>
  A Panel Figure contains an image that occupies a substantive space in the panel,
  typically filling edge to edge, and possibly even full bleed in the panel.
  We also have a modifier <code>.sage-panel__figure--wistia</code> for when Wistia videos are embedded in a figure.
</p>
<p><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
<div class="sage-panel-set">
  <%= render "examples/objects/panel/markup",
    body: %(
      <div class="sage-panel__block sage-type">
        <p>
          This panel shows a standard figure inside the it. No modifiers are added onto the base class.
        </p> 
      </div>
      <div class="sage-panel__figure">
    ) + image_pack_tag("docs/card/card-placeholder-lg.png", alt: "") + %(
      </div>
    ) + sample_copy
  %>
  <%= render "examples/objects/panel/markup",
    body: %(
